                     </div>
                  </div>
                  <div className="flex-1 space-y-10">
                     <span className="bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 text-[10px] font-black px-6 py-2 rounded-full uppercase tracking-[0.3em] shadow-sm">The Visionary</span>
                     <h2 className="text-6xl sm:text-8xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tighter leading-[0.9]">
                        Shopping, <span className="text-indigo-600">Perfected</span>.
                     </h2>
                     <div className="space-y-6">
                        <p className="text-2xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 font-bold leading-relaxed">
                          "I believe every household in Kenya deserves access to the world's best technology and hardware without the hassle of import logistics."
                        </p>
                        <p className="text-lg text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium">
                          From smart shower heads to the latest fashion from Farfetch, I personally select every item to ensure Susan's Market stands for quality and trust.
                        </p>
                     </div>
                     <div className="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 pt-8">
