            <h3 className="text-2xl font-black text-center text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">Check your phone</h3>
            <p className="text-center text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-bold leading-relaxed mb-10">
              An M-Pesa STK prompt has been sent to your device. Enter your PIN to pay <span className="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400">KES {total.toLocaleString()}</span> to Susan's Market.
            </p>
            <div className="space-y-4">
              <div className="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5">
                 <div className="flex justify-between text-[10px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">
                    <span>Receiver</span>
                    <span>Merchant ID</span>
